# ATM Banking System â€“ Java Console Application

##  Project Overview
This project is a console-based ATM Banking System developed using Java as part of the Java Development Internship at Coding Samurai.  
The application simulates basic ATM operations with a focus on clean logic, user interaction, and structured programming.

##  Features
- Check account balance
- Deposit money securely
- Withdraw money with balance validation
- Menu-driven interface for better user experience
- Graceful exit handling

##  Technologies Used
- Java (Core Java)
- Scanner class for user input
- Conditional statements and loops
- Modular method-based design

##  Concepts Implemented
- Variables and data types
- Methods and access modifiers
- Switch-case control structure
- Input validation and error handling

